WEBVTT

1
01:26:39.610 --> 01:26:43.400 
真美 是不? 这个月亮
It's beautiful, isn't it? The moon.

2
01:26:44.410 --> 01:26:45.820 
美极了
Divine.

3
01:26:46.500 --> 01:26:48.780 
好好享用了点睡前甜点 对不?
Had ourselves a little late-night snack, did we?

4
01:26:49.920 --> 01:26:53.500 
盒子就放在你床上 我想吃一颗也没大碍
It was on your bed, the box. I just thought I'd try one.

5
01:26:53.670 --> 01:26:57.170 
- 或者是吃20颗 - 我没有一刻不想她 哈利
- Or 20. - I can't stop thinking about her, Harry.

6
01:26:57.340 --> 01:26:59.330 
说实话 我还以为你觉得她烦了呢
Honestly, I reckoned she was annoying you.

7
01:26:59.510 --> 01:27:01.830 
她怎么可能会烦到我
She could never annoy me.

